column5: Hey guys me and my buddy (or two of them) have to go down to Ottawa and pick up my new boat in the next few weeks.  I'd LOVE to stop and fish Nip...anyone wanna host us for the day??   :D
I will but it will cost $1000 and I've never fished there
Gimme some dates if you can and I MIGHT be able to send ya in the right direction.... probably cost some minnows a java log and a handshake..
maybe you can rip out that middle bench if you have time!!!
I know Im pretty dumb with money....but....    That would not be a problem Randy
Your not allowed to say ass here!LOL
Gimme the dates, and I too might be able to help...
